  "special": {
    "title": "Octo means 9.",
    "description": "Fires a slow-moving 3x3 pellet grid that contracts toward the center and then spreads back out as it travels. The pellets move in a subtle sine-wave pattern, and the thrown Tediore reload still explodes on impact or after a short delay."
  },
  "notes": "During the $100,000 Loot Hunt, it was a featured drop from the Sheriff of Lynchwood alongside the Fastball, and a same-day hotfix boosted its damage. With the Gentle accessory, it fires 12 pellets, with four grid points carrying two pellets each. The doubled-up points can change between shots.",
